---
// HeroFocusHub.astro — Seção Hero da LP Focus Hub
---

<section class="fh-hero relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center pt-16 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Grid de fundo -->
  <div class="fh-hero-grid absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"></div>
  <!-- Blobs de brilho -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/3 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-[#0097D6]/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 left-1/3 w-72 h-72 bg-[#00D6A0]/8 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- Texto -->
      <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
        <!-- Badge -->
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#0097D6]/10 border border-[#0097D6]/30 text-[#0097D6] text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-8 fade-in-up" style="animation-delay:0s">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M11.3 1.046A1 1 0 0112 2v5h4a1 1 0 01.82 1.573l-7 10A1 1 0 018 18v-5H4a1 1 0 01-.82-1.573l7-10a1 1 0 011.12-.38z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
          </svg>
          Novo produto do IIT
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white leading-tight tracking-tight fade-in-up" style="animation-delay:0.15s">
          Sua cabeça não foi feita<br class="hidden sm:block" /> para guardar tarefas.<br />
          <span class="text-[#00D6A0]">O Focus Hub foi.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 leading-relaxed fade-in-up" style="animation-delay:0.28s">
          Focus Hub é o sistema GTD simplificado para profissionais e empreendedores que precisam capturar tudo, organizar com contexto e executar sem culpa — web e mobile, sempre sincronizados.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center lg:justify-start gap-4 fade-in-up" style="animation-delay:0.4s">
          <a
            href="#precos"
            class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-[#00D6A0] hover:bg-[#00A87E] text-[#0A0F14] font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-base shadow-lg shadow-[#00D6A0]/25 transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-105"
          >
            Começar grátis agora
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="#funcionalidades"
            class="w-full sm:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 border-2 border-white/20 text-white hover:border-[#0097D6] hover:text-[#0097D6] font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-base transition-all duration-200"
          >
            Ver como funciona
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Trust bar -->
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center lg:justify-start gap-5 text-sm text-gray-400 fade-in-up" style="animation-delay:0.5s">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="text-[#00D6A0] text-base">✓</span> Grátis para começar</span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="text-[#00D6A0] text-base">✓</span> Web + Mobile</span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><span class="text-[#00D6A0] text-base">✓</span> Sem cartão de crédito</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Mockup do app -->
      <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-end fade-in-up" style="animation-delay:0.3s">
        <div class="relative w-full max-w-md">
          <!-- Tela mockup estilizada -->
          <div class="bg-[#0D1B26] border border-[#0097D6]/30 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl shadow-black/50 overflow-hidden">
            <!-- Barra de título do app -->
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-3 border-b border-white/10">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">Focus Hub</span>
              <div class="flex gap-1.5">
                <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500/70"></span>
                <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/70"></span>
                <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500/70"></span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Conteúdo do app mockup -->
            <div class="p-5 space-y-3">
              <!-- Inbox item -->
              <div class="bg-[#0A0F14] border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#0097D6]"></span>
                  <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Inbox</span>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="w-4 h-4 border border-[#00D6A0] rounded flex-shrink-0"></span>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-300">Responder proposta do cliente</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="w-4 h-4 border border-[#00D6A0] rounded flex-shrink-0"></span>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-300">Revisar contrato Q1</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="w-4 h-4 bg-[#00D6A0] rounded flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                      <svg class="w-2.5 h-2.5 text-black" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                    </span>
                    <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 line-through">Atualizar planilha de metas</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Hábitos -->
              <div class="bg-[#0A0F14] border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-4">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#00D6A0]"></span>
                  <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Hábitos hoje</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex gap-2">
                  <div class="flex-1 text-center">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#00D6A0]/20 border-2 border-[#00D6A0] mx-auto flex items-center justify-center">
                      <span class="text-xs text-[#00D6A0]">✓</span>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1 block">Meditação</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex-1 text-center">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#00D6A0]/20 border-2 border-[#00D6A0] mx-auto flex items-center justify-center">
                      <span class="text-xs text-[#00D6A0]">✓</span>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1 block">Revisão</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex-1 text-center">
                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white/10 border-2 border-white/20 mx-auto"></div>
                    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1 block">Exercício</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Barra de progresso do dia -->
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">Progresso do dia</span>
                <div class="flex-1 bg-white/10 rounded-full h-1.5">
                  <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#0097D6] to-[#00D6A0] h-1.5 rounded-full" style="width: 67%"></div>
                </div>
                <span class="text-xs text-[#00D6A0] font-semibold">67%</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Glow decorativo sob o card -->
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-3/4 h-12 bg-[#00D6A0]/15 blur-xl rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scroll indicator -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .fh-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A0F14 0%, #0D1B26 55%, #0A1F2E 100%);
  }

  .fh-hero-grid {
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(0, 151, 214, 0.06) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 151, 214, 0.06) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
  }
</style>
